        public <T extends NftModel> NftCreateOperation createNftCreateOperationKt(java.lang.String symbol,

                                                                          kotlin.reflect.KClass<T> clazz,
                                                                          boolean transferable,
                                                                          Fee fee)

        Create NFT create operation. For more options see class NftCreateOperation constructor.

        Parameters:
        symbol - NFT symbol
        options - NFT options
        clazz - NFT model data class reference
        transferable - allow transfer of NFT data instances to other accounts
        fee - class Fee fee for the operation, by default the fee will be computed in DCT asset. When set to other then DCT, the request might fail if the asset is not convertible to DCT or conversion pool is not large enough
